<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <title>CSS Reftest Reference</title>
  <link rel="author" title="Hajime Shiozawa" href="mailto:hajime.shiozawa@gmail.com" />
  <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
    div#outer
    {
      color: orange;
      font: 3.75em/1.5 Ahem; /* computes to 60px/90px */
      width: 1.5em;
      text-align: center;
    }

    div {
      line-height: 1em;
    }
    div#blue90
    {
      color: blue;
      font-size: 1.5em; /* computes to 90px */
    }

    div#orange30
    {
      font-size: 0.5em; /* computes to 30px */
    }
    ]]></style>

  </head>

  <body>

  <p>Test passes if 2 orange squares are centered with respect to a blue square.</p>

  <div id="outer"><div>A</div><div id="blue90">B</div><div id="orange30">O</div></div>

  </body>
</html>
